channel.title: Indigoo’s Great Awesome Amazing Fairy Challenge
channel.description:
So I had an Idea today for a challenge:
_INDIGOO’S GREAT AWESOME AMAZING FAIRY CHALLENGE!_ -
So basically what you do is make a 30 second - 1 minute long track using just fairy. I don’t wanna torture you guys so uploading it to SoundCloud is not mandatory. Only posting the project here is fine. All submissions must be here by February 10th. Also, here’s a short project I made that might help you out: https://app.auxy.co/projects/oQViuu3uZS5j4ydrJ_wIfQ==
